# SoundCloud API Integration
# Get your token from: https://developers.soundcloud.com/docs/api/register-app
# 1. Create a SoundCloud account (Artist Pro required)
# 2. Register an app at https://soundcloud.com/you/apps
# 3. Use Client Credentials flow to get an access token
# 4. Paste the token below

VITE_SOUNDCLOUD_TOKEN=your_oauth_access_token_here
